{"tid":1077040,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分左手想被人屌醒既入一入黎","createTime":"2019-03-25T09:57:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T07:55:19.000Z","uid":133823,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1e89407367267b1abd622cbefd4a55c0a097ffa0","tid":1077040,"uid":133823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T09:57:00.000Z","msg":"好心你唔好咁撚戇鳩啦<br />\n唔係以為你做好d條女/仔就會返黎下話？<br />\n<br />\n人地一同你分手就係出面風流快活喇<br />\n留低你自己一個係屋企日日戇鳩鳩咁喊同亂諗<br />\n你覺得佢見到你咁會傷心呀？會同你一齊返呀？<br />\n人地唔關心你架喇懵撚<br />\n醒下啦柒頭皮<br />\n<br />\n條女/仔仲有搵你個d<br />\n唔好以為咁就有機復合啦好嘛？<br />\n人地未撚搵到下一個咪撚住你先囉<br />\n一有新既人埋身<br />\n你地就賤過地底泥<br />\n乜撚野都唔係呀<br />\n<br />\n充實下自己增值下自己<br />\n唔好衰比條臭閪/厹睇<br />\n你地未來一定會搵到更好既人<br />\n<br />\n最後想同d臭閪/厹講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好以為做咁多仆街野冇報應</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他朝君體也相同</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地唔會有好結果</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利伸: 啱啱撞到佢同條厹玩得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1fc06187e375301f9141f7788abf184eff9655","tid":1077040,"uid":15957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"佢冇 <br />\n<br />\n我諗我地大家都係里埋on on99緊"},{"pid":"836aedb0ed15a2f80e9e07282c7c15149bd94c5f","tid":1077040,"uid":133823,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"bd1fc06187e375301f9141f7788abf184eff9655","tid":1077040,"uid":15957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:05:02.000Z","msg":"佢冇 <br />\n<br />\n我諗我地大家都係里埋on on99緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"冇又點？<br />\n係咪代表佢呢一世都會就咁收收埋埋就算？<br />\n佢都會識過第二個<br />\n佢都會有自己既新生活<br />\n唔好再諗住大家收收埋埋就一世<br />\n<br />\n巴打唔好再懷緬過去<br />\n就算佢以前點好都好<br />\n所有野已經過左去<br />\n<br />\n如果有一日佢話一齊返既<br />\n諗清楚大家問題解決未<br />\n解決左當然好<br />\n未解決就唔好咁快應承<br />\n如果佢唔返黎既<br />\n做好你自己搵過個更好既<br />\nYou deserve better<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35fda4dca6e9d85fc0c4fd45f7a7d681dc01c125","tid":1077040,"uid":133823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f93a74c7fa910eaea141a33892365e1b9d0f4845","tid":1077040,"uid":155360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"點先搵到下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1017ff37031da9f413a416e26f692fdd22d4d1bd","tid":1077040,"uid":76697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7620a4d746f18f05cbe475fe383c211c5079deaa","tid":1077040,"uid":133823,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f93a74c7fa910eaea141a33892365e1b9d0f4845","tid":1077040,"uid":155360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:48:59.000Z","msg":"點先搵到下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"諗黎都冇用<br />\n要黎既始終會黎<br />\n你可以做既就係prepare好自己迎接佢既到來<br />\n<br />\n諗下係啱啱個段感情裏面學到d咩<br />\n做得差既就改左佢<br />\n做得好既就keep住<br />\n<br />\n學多d唔同既野<br />\n識多d唔同既人<br />\n可能你會係呢d新圈子入面識到你既下一個"},{"pid":"937b0f1957eade21408e2b65991650c605afa491","tid":1077040,"uid":133823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1017ff37031da9f413a416e26f692fdd22d4d1bd","tid":1077040,"uid":76697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:45:42.000Z","msg":"咁你離開啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1225e42e542ea0c3d35dd9ef888c2a907cc6fba8","tid":1077040,"uid":177916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1017ff37031da9f413a416e26f692fdd22d4d1bd","tid":1077040,"uid":76697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T12:12:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"